original_title: Claire Castel & Jessyca Wilson: 2 salopes en club
overview: Tonight, Claire and Jessyca do a sexy show in a night club. While getting ready and rehearsing, the DJ and one of the bartenders come to get an good view. The two girls decide it's time to relax and have some fun with these two guys. It all ends in a foursome the two men will never forget.
title: Claire Castel & Jessyca Wilson: 2 salopes en club
